Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.01,0:01:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Dispel the Genjutsu, and wake up Naruto and Shikamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.76,0:01:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first mission we've had in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.26,0:01:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.18,0:01:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Proceed with caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.27,0:01:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an A-Rank mission just like the mission in the Land of Waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.73,0:01:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.87,0:01:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You were able to repel Genjutsu, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.58,0:01:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why were you pretending to be asleep?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.37,0:02:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Go after Sasuke and once you meet up with him, stop Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.52,0:02:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then await new orders in a safe place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.58,0:02:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Sasuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.80,0:02:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you while we move.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.34,0:02:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, so that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.52,0:02:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn Sasuke... He got too hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So why did I get sent out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How troublesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.29,0:02:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were Kakashi-sensei's orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How long will it take for us to catch up with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He is moving pretty fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.71,0:03:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.45,0:03:16.46,Sign_1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(243,233)}Coward no. 1
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.45,0:03:16.46,Sign_1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(480,538)}It's troublesome, but I've got to do it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Coward no. 1\NIt's Troublesome, but I've got to do it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Increase your speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find Sasuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.29,0:03:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Two platoons, a total of eight people, are behind us...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I sense another one...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.09,0:03:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So nine guys are coming after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, man... Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:03:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They haven't found our exact location yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.04,0:04:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But we'll have to lose them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Why did you stop?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet, and follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Step backwards onto your footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it will look like our footsteps have suddenly disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But... even if we do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll still figure out what we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll buy us some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.89,0:05:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.12,0:05:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, the pursuers will become impatient and that will create a weakness in their pursuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.52,0:05:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If they don't see the clues that lead to us, even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.84,0:05:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.77,0:05:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gaining on us even though they're being careful and looking out for any ambushes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:06:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They all must be above Chuunin level.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.35,0:06:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If they catch up to us, we'll be annihilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Annihilated...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.21,0:06:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we should stop and hide to ambush them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambush?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If we ambush them, we'll have an advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they have two times more guys than us...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It might work if we catch them off guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the men of the former Konoha ninja, Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Worst case is that there is a Jounin among them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.58,0:06:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that would've worked... But it won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy's level doesn't matter when you're ambushing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys sure don't understand, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that ambushing is a really advantageous basic tactic...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But to pull it off, there are two conditions you must meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And what are those conditions?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,First, the runner must move silently, and must discover the enemy first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Second, we must secure a location to catch the pursuers off guard and inflict critical damage to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and quickly conceal ourselves in that location.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we're able to fulfill those conditions an ambush becomes a valid tactic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If we have the ninja dog's nose, we can find their location pretty easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,As for the second one, it seems that we're at an advantage since this is our village, and we know the terrain better...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.84,0:07:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But Orochimaru has been in Konoha before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're dealing with his men, that method won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So what are you trying to get at?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.06,0:07:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The pursuers have been taught about the terrain and have most likely gone through training for this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, they are all most likely ninja who have mastered the art of pursuing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So they know how we'll act.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.38,0:08:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambushing is still advantageous, but\N there are too many uncertain factors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.86,0:08:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, the enemy is a squadron organized specifically for this plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.63,0:08:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,As for us, we have an idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,a female ninja who has no special traits...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,a dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and the number one coward, me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A strategy is devised by understanding the situation, and creating the best plan for that situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.25,0:08:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one thing we can do right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.46,0:08:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A feint operation that looks like an ambush.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,One person will stay behind, set up things to look like an ambush and stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So... play the decoy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.55,0:08:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:09:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If the person can stop them, they won't be able to get the location of the other three.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we can lose the pursuers, but the decoy will most likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So, who wants to take the job?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.53,0:09:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We need the dog to look for Sasuke, which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.23,0:10:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...the only choice left is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Shikamaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.76,0:10:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better than being annihilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.22,0:10:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, the only guy who can pull of this decoy perfectly and have a high chance of surviving withing this group...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.61,0:10:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kagemane no jutsu was originally made to stop the enemy anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.95,0:10:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll catch up with you guys later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you, Shikamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Was Shikamaru such a reliable guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful... Shikamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you can mask your presence...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.91,0:11:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,we see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:11:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, the enemy is getting closer and closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.12,0:12:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.80,0:12:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he really stopping the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.55,0:12:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and the number one coward, me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Shikamaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.19,0:12:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Shikamaru will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.27,0:12:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't run away, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you! He'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.29,0:12:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.31,0:12:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He's foul-mouthed, and he's lazy, but he'll never betray another person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He rarely does things on his own, but when he does, he'll do it all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can guarantee that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.24,0:12:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to believe that... I want to, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to raise our speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I was able to run away nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The footstep intervals are irregular.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.72,0:13:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Their impatience must be increasing their fatigue.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I was supposed to be the number one coward...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but it seems like my character is a bit different this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.05,0:13:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that I'm fatigued, but you're wrong about the footprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.35,0:13:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what made those paw prints.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still only a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.15,0:13:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that we fell for this trick...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the Kageshibari no jutsu of Konoha that I've heard about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an old way of saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.46,0:14:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Times have passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They call it Kagemane now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.19,0:14:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That match I had is having a bad effect on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I used up too much chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't last much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.53,0:14:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,five, six, seven, eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.83,0:14:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eight people...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, I sense another one...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So nine are coming after us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.51,0:14:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So the ninth was the escort to protect these guys from an ambush.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.85,0:15:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who keeps a constant distance between them, travels behind them, and deals with an enemy ambush.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.28,0:15:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But this will make it clear where he's hiding!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.59,0:15:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.18,0:15:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.67,0:15:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My shadow won't reach there...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any more stamina to convert to chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.60,0:15:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.91,0:15:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We know how your technique works.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.07,0:15:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.99,0:15:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you've reached your limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This Kagemane thing will go away soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:15:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You better be prepared for what's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.05,0:16:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,just wanted to do this ninja thing normally, get paid normally...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,get married with a woman who's neither ugly nor beautiful and have two children.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The first one would be a girl, and the next would be a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I would retire from my ninja job after my daughter gets married, and my son gets a job...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I would play Shogi and Go during the boring days, and live free from worldly cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I would die from old age before my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the kind of life I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But I made too much of an effort, which was very unlike me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to die a normal way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.96,0:16:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotten myself into something troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:17:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The pursuers have stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.01,0:17:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.57,0:17:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He succeeded in stopping them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.43,0:17:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be Shikamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that I doubted you even a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.40,0:17:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.82,0:17:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.02,0:17:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Also... Shikamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.24,0:17:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You better be alive and catch up to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you said, I've reached my limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.85,0:17:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And pop off his head while you're at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.79,0:18:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally caught up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuma? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.43,0:18:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Shikamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.52,0:19:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't my thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll retire from this for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What a persistent guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.09,0:19:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We have extra pursuers now... Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, three.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.73,0:19:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Kankuro, we're going to pick up our pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.60,0:19:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.73,0:20:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get too hasty, Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.32,0:20:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's begin.
