Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.21,0:21:15.43,ED4,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}it's nothing to be ashamed of
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.43,0:21:20.73,ED4,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Don't let this scar go to waste
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:26.37,ED4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)\blur3}Be able to smile as you walk
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.71,0:21:41.96,ED4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)\blur3}Yes, breathe in the air\NLift your face to the sky and jump
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.96,0:21:47.15,ED4,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}If it rains, take a break\NGo where the wind takes you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.15,0:21:52.39,ED4,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So many regrets\NDon't let this scar go to waste
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.39,0:21:57.63,ED4,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Let's go carve the badges in our chest\NYes, it's show time, life begins now
