Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.43,0:22:18.65,ED4,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Be able to smile as you walk
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.65,0:22:29.13,ED4,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Turn your sadness into wind and continue to move forward
